<p>Hello <%= @participant.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  Thank you for registering for the European Go Congress 2027. An account for
  this email address already exists, but you still need to confirm this
  registration. Please do so below.
</p>

<p>
  If you did not make this registration and suspect someone is trying to abuse
  your email address, please contact us at <%= mail_to "info@egc2027.nl" %>.
</p>

<p>Here are the details you provided:</p>

<p>
  <strong>Name:</strong> <%= @participant.first_name %> <%= @participant.last_name %><br>
  <strong>Country:</strong> <%= @participant.country %><br>
  <% if @participant.club.present? %>
    <strong>Club:</strong> <%= @participant.club %><br>
  <% end %>
  <% if @participant.rank_grade.present? %>
    <strong>Rank:</strong> <%= @participant.rank_grade %><br>
  <% end %>
  <% if @participant.rating.present? %>
    <strong>Rating:</strong> <%= @participant.rating %><br>
  <% end %>
  <strong>Congress Pass:</strong> <%= @participant.attendance_option&.humanize || "—" %>
</p>

<p>Please confirm your registration by clicking the link below:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Confirm Registration", @confirmation_url %></p>

<p>
  If you have any questions, please contact us at
  <%= mail_to "info@egc2027.nl" %>.
</p>
